{'id_' : 'ho|s03_nde_zim_oaz|hoMA|SunPostGospel|text', 'text' : 'Kukho lokhu sesikubonile ukuvuka kukaKhristu, kasikhonzeni iNkosi engcwele uJesu Khristu, yena yedwa ongela sono. Sikhonza isiphambano sakho, Khristu, njalo ukuvuka kwakho siyakudumisa sihlabelela, ngoba unguNkulunkulu wethu ngakho asazi omunye ngaphandle kwakho, sibiza igama lakho. Wozani lonke bazalwane sikhonze ukuvuka kukaKhristu okungcwele. Ngoba Nkosi ngesiphambano intokozo yaza emhlabeni kasiyibusiseni  kokuphela iNkosi, kasihlabeleni ukuvuka kwakhe ngoba wahlupheka esiphambanweni wakunqoba ukufa ngokufa.'}
